data.description: Featuring a spacious open kitchen and family room, this home has a formal living and dining area, a versatile loft, and a 2 car garage. This home offers a wealth of upgrades, including stunning laminate/hardwood flooring, Energy Star certified appliances, granite countertops, recessed lighting, 42' cabinets, 9-foot ceilings, a deluxe master bath with a garden tub, separate shower, dual sinks, and a spacious backyard to be enjoyed.
